EmailTemplate.name: Process Change : ValidFill Conversion Kits for CCFS 9000
EmailTemplate.subject: New ValidFill Kit Process
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!User.FirstName},
We are changing the process to get ValidFill conversion kits for CCFS 9000.
Previously the kits were shipped with the equipment package. Moving forward all kits will be supplied by ValidFill.
Enclosed is the new process and the communication form that should be sent to ValidFill by the COM. All steps should be completed by the COM unless they choose to delegate the work to the Sales Support PM as part of the installation project.
Thank You,
National Customer & Field Operations
Freestyle Operations
